HEADWORD: Solisequious
<hw>Sol`i*se"qui*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>sol</ets> sun + <ets>sequi</ets> to follow.]</ety> <def>Following
the course of the sun; <as>as, <ex>solisequious</ex> plants</as>.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Sir T. Browne.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
